Subject: Add flags to 'it list' to show tickets of a certain type only
Issuer: Vincent Driessen <vincent@datafox.nl>
Date: 2009-05-22 07:11:22
Type: feature
Priority: 2
Status: open
Assigned to: -

For example
	it list -b	should show open bugs only;
	it list -f	should show all features, etc.;
	it list -ba	should show all bugs, including closed ones.
